{"text": " You Now prepare for round 5, in which you will be guiding yourself to connect with your center of gravity. Use your vertical exhalation to help you reach your central gravity effectively. At some point of the practice you may release the exhaling and any breathing and just fully connect and maintain the link with the center of gravity. And as thoughts arise, drive them back to the center of gravity. We shall begin round 5, in 3, 2, 1.", "segments": [{"id": 0, "seek": 0, "start": 1.8000000000000003, "end": 2.0, "text": " You", "tokens": [50364, 509, 50464], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.976608157157898, "compression_ratio": 0.2727272727272727, "no_speech_prob": 0.2570077180862427, "words": [{"word": " You", "start": 1.8000000000000003, "end": 2.5, "probability": 0.0031327442266047}]}, {"id": 1, "seek": 3000, "start": 40.06, "end": 53.38, "text": " Now prepare for round 5, in which you will be guiding yourself to connect with your", "tokens": [50364, 823, 5940, 337, 3098, 1025, 11, 294, 597, 291, 486, 312, 25061, 1803, 281, 1745, 365, 428, 51532], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.3253734679449172, "compression_ratio": 1.064102564102564, "no_speech_prob": 0.03155020251870155, "words": [{"word": " Now", "start": 40.06, "end": 40.82, "probability": 0.8617602586746216}, {"word": " prepare", "start": 40.82, "end": 41.34, "probability": 0.9414364099502563}, {"word": " for", "start": 41.34, "end": 41.72, "probability": 0.9956739544868469}, {"word": " round", "start": 41.72, "end": 42.0, "probability": 0.8911677002906799}, {"word": " 5,", "start": 42.0, "end": 42.7, "probability": 0.5355142951011658}, {"word": " in", "start": 43.66, "end": 47.74, "probability": 0.8955496549606323}, {"word": " which", "start": 47.74, "end": 48.02, "probability": 0.9981850981712341}, {"word": " you", "start": 48.02, "end": 48.26, "probability": 0.8526315093040466}, {"word": " will", "start": 48.26, "end": 48.44, "probability": 0.9922938346862793}, {"word": " be", "start"